description.en: Australian Safe Shepherd is a community meme token forked from the infamous safemoon. The token is completely community driven and was fair launched. Every trade continues toward automatically generating liquidity locked inside of PancakeSwap's LP. Holders earn passive rewards through static reflection as they watch their balance of "ASS" indefinitely grow.
